elivery of women’s services that focus on entrepreneurship and supportive self-help programs that lead to their independence, self-empowerment and success.\r\n\r\nAs a Life Coach, my goal is to assist individuals to achieve healthy and productive lives. Through my education, personal experience and professional training, my focus and mission is to help individuals heal and release any psychological obstacles that may prevent them from achieving their goals and living their dreams.\r\n\r\nMy experiences as a mother, widow, businesswoman and caregiver have shaped my perspective on life in that I find fulfillment in helping others actualize their dreams. I firmly believe that one can serve others better if one shares personal experiences. With all the joys in my life, I developed my greatest strengths from my challenges, as well as my tragedies. I am a survivor, and my life is now happier than I thought possible.\r\n\r\nFrom Now On was established with the vision to help others in need and to guide them through life’s challenges. Working together, I will share with you what life has taught me and help you to discover your path to happiness and fulfillment.','Who We Are','','publish','open','open','','who-we-are','','','2012-02-01 12:36:25','2012-02-01 17:36:25','',0,'http://fromnowon.ca/wp-draft1-s/?page_id=23',2,'page','',0);
INSERT INTO `bo1e_posts` VALUES (8,1,'2011-02-08 21:02:08','2011-02-09 02:02:08','In addition to her work with <strong>From Now On</strong> and <strong>Peel Collaborative Law Practice Group  she is  a </strong> Trainer of <strong>PNDC (Power Non-Defensive Communication).</strong>Vittoria is also a Financial Advisor and Owner of <strong>Adhami &amp; Adhami Financial Group</strong>. She has had a wide and varied career and her educational background is extensive.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Harvard Law School, Boston USA</strong>\r\nMediator Certificate</li>\r\n	<li><strong>IACP International Academy  Of  Collaborative Professionals\r\n</strong>Associate Professional of Peel Collaborative Law Practice Group</li>\r\n	<li><strong>York University</strong>\r\nHonours Degree, Psychology</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Financial Services Commission of Ontario</strong>\r\nFinancial Advisor</li>\r\n	<li><strong>National Guild Of Hypnosis</strong>\r\nHypnosis &amp; NLP Certificate</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Rome Italy</strong>\r\nTeaching  Certificate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to her volunteer work with <a href=\"http://costi.org/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">COSTI Immigrant Services (costi.org)</a>, Vittoria conducts a number of self-empowerment workshops for immigrant women facing barriers. She is also a recipient of the <strong>Province of Ontario Volunteer Award.</strong>\r\n\r\nVittoria is fluent in English and Italian, with proficiency in both French and Farsi.\r\n\r\n[youtube url=\"http://youtu.be/lsDpQbBA8p4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" autohide=\"1\" controls=\"1\" disablekb=\"1\" fs=\"1\" hd=\"1\" rel=\"0\" showsearch=\"0\"]','Credentials','','publish','open','closed','','credentials','','','2012-04-02 09:45:21','2012-04-02 13:45:21','',0,'http://fromnowon.ca/wp-draft1-s',4,'page','',0);
