INSERT INTO `bo1e_posts` VALUES (59,1,'2011-10-27 10:30:02','2011-10-27 14:30:02','Seamlessly enhance technically sound potentialities and high-payoff ROI. Enthusiastically evolve intuitive vortals vis-a-vis empowered value. Enthusiastically seize cross-unit data rather than technically sound information. Synergistically architect granular architectures whereas 24/7 core competencies. \r\n\r\nCompetently aggregate customer directed methodologies before global catalysts for change. Energistically impact highly efficient process improvements through process-centric partnerships. Assertively seize open-source niche markets for cost effective mindshare. Intrinsicly foster plug-and-play technologies and collaborative alignments. \r\n\r\nMonotonectally revolutionize front-end processes whereas an expanded array of resources. Authoritatively redefine equity invested niches rather than cutting-edge content. Interactively leverage existing client-focused users through leveraged growth strategies. Energistically seize virtual potentialities before go forward information. \r\n\r\nInteractively brand cutting-edge sources vis-a-vis ubiquitous networks. Appropriately productize interactive methodologies via progressive users. Quickly expedite granular architectures via superior human capital. Globally myocardinate world-class leadership skills vis-a-vis client-focused technologies. \r\n\r\nConveniently fabricate superior quality vectors through holistic e-commerce. Completely expedite long-term high-impact best practices with bricks-and-clicks synergy. Professionally network fully tested benefits after equity invested materials. Professionally productize revolutionary total linkage whereas interoperable outsourcing. \r\n\r\nConveniently visualize focused networks and next-generation core competencies. Credibly whiteboard fully tested communities before frictionless relationships. Proactively predominate emerging human capital for process-centric services. Phosfluorescently simplify excellent core competencies after frictionless materials. \r\n\r\nObjectively e-enable cost effective communities with premier ROI. Interactively unleash customized methodologies via functionalized materials. Assertively conceptualize multidisciplinary meta-services through parallel best practices. Monotonectally deliver client-centered ROI via emerging collaboration and idea-sharing. \r\n\r\nAssertively maintain worldwide initiatives before out-of-the-box convergence. Rapidiously fashion client-focused schemas through team driven strategic theme areas. Enthusiastically productize installed base results after customer directed paradigms. Dramatically seize cost effective applications with strategic infrastructures.','Intercultural Marriages','','inherit','open','open','','48-revision-3','','','2011-10-27 10:30:02','2011-10-27 14:30:02','',48,'http://fromnowon.ca/wp-draft1-s/48-revision-3.html',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `bo1e_posts` VALUES (60,1,'2011-10-27 10:33:47','2011-10-27 14:33:47','<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-331\" title=\"coaching3\" src=\"http://fromnowon.ca/wp-draft1-s/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/coaching3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\nLife coaching helps individuals identify and achieve personal goals.  At <strong>From Now On Life Coaching</strong> the focus is on <em>your goals!</em>  Using a variety of tools and techniques, we help you to solve problems, develop peak performance, create and grow with change and most importantly, welcome and embrace change.\r\n\r\nAvailable to individuals and groups, in person, over the phone and online, our commitment is to provide you with an environment that allows you to freely express your inner self to help you address some difficult questions such as why you act a certain way, what stops you from making a change and what motivates you to take action.\r\n\r\nFrom Now On specializes in one-to-one coaching sessions that help you fast-forward your personal development and acquire the necessary skills that will enrich your personal, social and working life.\r\n\r\nLife Coaching is not an easy fix – it is a process that encourages an individual to achieve change from deep within, the type of change that lasts a life time. Once we have helped you to discover your strengths, we teach you to use them and then encourage to you walk alone – strong, proud, and full of anticipation for what life has to offer you!','Life Coaching','','publish','open','open','','life-coaching','','','2012-04-11 20:56:37','2012-04-12 00:56:37','',20,'http://fromnowon.ca/wp-draft1-s/?page_id=60',1,'page','',0);
