apped in a Diamond here.</a></p>\r\n<h2>Life Coaching</h2>\r\n<h3>What employers look for in an employee</h3>\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/9-384hIv3xY?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<h3>About Vittoria\'s Workshop</h3>\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\"  src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/UqLxAbh6EMk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/_YP983IFCk4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe> -->\r\n\r\n','Media','','inherit','open','open','','29-revision-21','','','2014-10-22 20:31:48','2014-10-23 00:31:48','',29,'http://fromnowon.ca/29-revision-21.html',0,'revision','',0);
